title: DPS-BEST OF- Oct 13, 2020
itunes:title: DPS-BEST OF- Oct 13, 2020
description:
On Today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Quarterback duel between Justin Herbert and Drew Brees. Is the new wave of QB officially here? We're joined by "First Things First" co-host Nick Wright, Washington Football Team QB Alex Smith and Former Cy Young award winner CC Sabathia. Plus, we take a hard left turn into some Music talk.
